'''Sarvel Tal-Oldra''' was a [[Corellian/Legends|Corellian]] who once worked for the [[Cozzell Corporation]]. He was one of the designers for the company's advanced [[Juggernaut 510 Combat Power Armor]]. When the project was shut down due to the immense cost of integrating the armor's varied components, Tal-Oldra took offense and began producing suits of Juggernaut armor in the [[Corporate Sector/Legends|Corporate Sector]] [[Outlaw tech/Legends|outlaw tech]] base formerly run by [[Klaus Vandangante/Legends|Klaus "Doc" Vandangante]].

